      • openUrlIfDifferent

        public void openUrlIfDifferent(java.lang.String pageKey,
                               java.util.List<GherkinStepCondition> conditions)
                        throws TechnicalException,
                               FailureException
        Open Url if different with conditions.
        Parameters:
        pageKey - is the key of page (example: SALTO_HOME)
        conditions - list of 'expected' values condition and 'actual' values (GherkinStepCondition).
        Throws:
        TechnicalException - is thrown if you have a technical error (format, configuration, datas, ...) in NoraUi. Exception with "FAIL_MESSAGE_UNABLE_TO_OPEN_APPLICATION" message (with screenshot, with exception)
        FailureException - if the scenario encounters a functional error

      • switchWindow

        public void switchWindow(java.lang.String windowKey,
                         java.util.List<GherkinStepCondition> conditions)
                  throws TechnicalException,
                         FailureException
        Switch window when the scenario contain more one windows (one more application for example).
        Parameters:
        windowKey - the key of window (popup, ...) Example: OSCAR.
        conditions - list of 'expected' values condition and 'actual' values (GherkinStepCondition).
        Throws:
        TechnicalException - is thrown if you have a technical error (format, configuration, datas, ...) in NoraUi. Exception with "FAIL_MESSAGE_UNABLE_TO_SWITCH_WINDOW" message (with screenshot, with exception)
        FailureException - if the scenario encounters a functional error
